room_title: Escape room "The Millionaire's Loft" by Escape House Mesa in Phoenix
room_description: You are loft-sitting for your Uncle who is out of town. The maintenance crew is coming in to change the cameras. Since the cameras will be off for the next hour, your uncle wants you to sit in his loft until they are back online. Rumor has it, he stores a lot of cash in the room. Can you find his loot before the cameras come back on?
